---
title: Red Thai Style Coconut Prawn Curry  with Zesty Jasmine Rice and Salted Peanuts
description: Red chillies give Thai Red its signature colour, as well as its flavour and heat! Here, our Red Thai Style Prawn Coconut Curry is loaded with prawns, veg and chickpeas in a curried coconut milk base for a hearty dinner.
